Package application

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AvatarDrawingController
    Handles events for avatar drawing page.
    CheckoutController
    CheckoutController is a class that controls the checkout system GUI and the functions behind it.
    CopyController
    The gui that appears when a resource is clicked, shows the information about a resource and allows the user to request a copy if there is a free copy available.
    EditCopiesController
    EditCopiesController is a class that creates a GUI for the librarian to edit the copies table.
    ExplorerRow
    Class used to store attributes for filling in the Copies explorer table in the staff tab.
    LoginController
    This class allows user or librarians to log in to the library system.
    Main  
    MainFX  
    ProfileController
    Profile Controller is responsible for handling events within the library resources, my profile, and staff profile tabs.
    RecommendedController
    Recommend controller is a class that deals with showing our extra feature, the recommended resource feature.
    RegisterController
    This class allows user to register into the library system.
    ResourceAdderController
    Resourceadder is the controller for the GUI which allows a librarian to insert a new resource.
    ResourceController
    Resource Controller is a class that setups up the resources and updates them.
    ScreenManager
    ScreenManager is a class that helps us get variables from the database to use in our scenes.
    StaffBalanceController
    Controller for StaffBalance view.
    StaffEdit
    This class allows staff/librarians to view and edit their details when they register to the system.
    TransactionsController
    Controller for the transactions view.
